listen and learn.  Also the noise in the background of this file was 
a pretty good thunderstorm we were having here in NJ and you can 
hear the thunder during the &quot;Sumption&quot; part.  I find i get the best 
results during storms and any kind of bad weather, they seem more 
talkative than for some reason.  It must be the electricity from the 
storm that they can feed off of to gain more control of the box.

Just a guess, i really don&#39;t know why it&#39;s better during storms.

